<div class="com-share" data-id="6956" data-title="《在奥斯卡上安慰石头姐的乐高小金人是谁做的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6956/medium/6956.jpg?1436698068" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6956.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
